<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

    <style>
        /* General about section styling */
        .about {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            /* Light background */
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            /* Dark text */
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        /* Headings styling */
        .abt-h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #434240;
            /* Dark blue heading */
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            /* text-transform: uppercase; */
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .about b {
            display: block;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            color: #e59400;
            /* Blue for emphasis */
            margin: 20px 0 10px 0;
        }

        .about p.abt-p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #555;
            /* Dark grey for readability */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        /* List styling for team members */
        .about ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .about ul li {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Add a decorative icon next to list items */
        .about ul li::before {
            content: '•';
            color: #e59400;
            /* Icon color */
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
        }

        /* Responsive styling */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .abt-h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .about b {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }

            .about p.abt-p,
            .about ul li {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }

        /* Optional styling for the section */
        .about p,
        .about ul li {
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>

    <div class="about">

        <h2 class="abt-h2">WANDERER </h2>
        <b>Discover Your Next Adventure with Wanderer</b>
        <p class="abt-p">
            Welcome to Wanderer—where your journey begins. We're more than just a travel website. we're your gateway to
            the world's most captivating destinations. Our passion is to inspire, inform, and ignite your wanderlust
            with curated experiences and insider knowledge.
        </p>
        <b>Our Mission</b>

        <p class="abt-p">At Wanderer, we believe that travel is more than just a destination; it's an opportunity to
            connect, explore, and grow. Our mission is to make every journey unforgettable by providing you with
            personalized travel guides, local insights, and tips that transform ordinary trips into extraordinary
            adventures.</p>

        <b>Our Story</b>
        <p class="abt-p">Wanderer was born out of a deep-seated love for exploration and a desire to share the magic of
            travel with the world. It all started with a group of friends who embarked on a road trip across Europe,
            documenting their experiences and discovering hidden gems along the way. What began as a personal project
            quickly evolved into a passion to help others experience the joy of discovery.</p>

        <b>Meet the Team</b>
        <ul>
            <li> <b>Hadwrsha Baro</b> <i>Co-Founder & Travel Enthusiast</i> : Hadwrsha’s love for off-the-beaten-path
                destinations and local cuisines drives our content. With a background in cultural studies, he’s
                dedicated to showcasing authentic experiences. </li>
            <li> <b>Upangkar Baro</b> <i>Co-Founder & Tech</i> : Upangkar ensures that Wanderer’s technology runs
                seamlessly, making your travel planning smooth and enjoyable. His knack for innovation helps us provide
                cutting-edge tools for your journey.</li>
            <li> <b>Daoharu Basumatary</b> <i>Manager & Explorer</i> : Douharu’s travel stories and photography capture the
                essence of each destination. His adventures bring to life the vibrant cultures and landscapes we
                feature.</li>
        </ul>

        <b>What Sets Us Apart</b>
        <p class="abt-p"> Wanderer stands out with our commitment to providing unique, tailored travel experiences. We
            go beyond generic recommendations, offering personalized itineraries and local guides who share their
            insider knowledge. Our goal is to help you uncover the true spirit of each place you visit, whether it’s a
            bustling city, a serene village, or a stunning natural wonder.</p>

        <b>Join the Journey</b>
        <p class="abt-p">Ready to explore the world with us? Follow Wanderer on social media, sign up for our
            newsletter, or reach out to share your travel dreams. We're here to guide you every step of the way and
            ensure your adventures are nothing short of spectacular.</p>

    </div>